Of course, I talk to her in the middle of the night when the absence hurts too much, she invites herself into my dreams when the mood is a little reached.
We feel carried and protected in the difficult times, the retrospect of time makes us realize how much she was a conductor and we try to stay on the path she had drawn us.
If a being has loved you very strongly, the absence cannot rip it from your heart and memories.
